originalText.text: I’ve been doing virtual personal training with Andrew Schaeffer of Utmost for almost 2 years, now. I was skeptical at first about whether virtual training could work, but it’s been great and I’ve seen so many positive changes. I can’t say enough good things about him! Andrew does not do cookie-cutter training, but rather individualized training tailored to both long term goals and the aches and pains of the day. And he’s a really nice person, too!

originalText.text:
I have been working with Andrew for personal training at Utmost for over 10 years and could not be more pleased. He listens to my goals and helps me monitor progress. He is very responsive to specific needs; I just had surgery and we worked on the sensitive surgical area, carefully and successfully.
His extensive knowledge of physiology is key.
He is also flexible and reasonable, understanding that I am as busy as he is.
If you are on the Upper Westside of Manhattan (New York City) I'd recommend you meet with Andrew and discuss your plan.

originalText.text: I have been a client of Andrew for many years and he is exceptional.  He always focuses on proper form and works with each client to meet his/her goals while monitoring that he/she performs each exercise safely and with proper alignment. He is very professional and has a wonderful personality that makes him a pleasure to work with.
